et him into society?'\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 358, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"score\": 0.9997135139514457, \"rank\": 0.0002777106673353038, \"text\": \"Zac\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 how canI get him there?\\\"\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how canI\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eric Murray is talking to Sonia Gray on this week's episode ofNo Such Thing as Normal, aNZ Heraldpodcast about neurodiversity.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M.O.P.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 6.587386562020161e-13, \"text\": \"Eric Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M.O.P.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M.O.P.\"}, {\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sonia_Fowler\", \"score\": 0.9999999954038685, \"rank\": 4.593877778171534e-09, \"text\": \"Sonia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sonia_Fowler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sonia_Fowler\"}, {\"begin\": 459, \"end\": 463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Edward_Gray\", \"score\": 0.9998924061484741, \"rank\": 5.518097548874525e-05, \"text\": \"Gray\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Edward_Gray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Edward_Gray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this week's episode ofNo Such Thing\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"Normal\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"Heraldpodcast\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"neurodiversity\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His 12-year-old son Zac is autistic with ADHD, and is non-speaking.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 574, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"score\": 0.9997135139514457, \"rank\": 0.0002777106673353038, \"text\": \"Zac\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His 12-year-old son\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"ADHD\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some of it's so rewarding, and then other times you want to sit in the shower and have a cry\\\", he says.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shower\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"a cry\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has to be 'eyes on the prize' 24/7, so I incorporate Zac into everything I do.\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 785, \"end\": 788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"score\": 0.9997135139514457, \"rank\": 0.0002777106673353038, \"text\": \"Zac\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eyes\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have our routine, which he needs.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our routine\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he also likes being in new environments.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new environments\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And he will look around, he takes it all in, he's just looking at everything.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he has a photographic memory, he's like Jason Bourne, he probably knows exactly how many steps it is to the front door.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Bourne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.877061693719759e-24, \"text\": \"Jason Bourne\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Bourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Bourne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a photographic memory\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly how many steps\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1071}, {\"ngram\": \"the front door\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he will not tell me.\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He can not tell me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The father and son try and get out in the community as much as possible, but Zac can be impulsive and is easily dysregulated, which means meltdowns in public are common.\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"score\": 0.9997135139514457, \"rank\": 0.0002777106673353038, \"text\": \"Zac\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The father\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"son\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"meltdowns\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most people in Cambridge know them, and are understanding, but occasionally the response from the passersby is less than helpful.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Cambridge\", \"score\": 0.9950811588384509, \"rank\": 0.004943155659737615, \"text\": \"Cambridge\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Cambridge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Cambridge\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Most people\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"the response\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"the passersby\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of it is they just do not know, the intimate details around, like what having a child with autism or ADHD neurodiverse.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"the intimate details\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"autism\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"ADHD neurodiverse\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They do not know the stresses,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stresses\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But if you see a kid yelling, or stimming (self-stimulating behaviours such as repetitive body movements) or having a meltdown, it's not helpful to say 'control your kid!'.\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a kid yelling\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"(self-stimulating behaviours\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"repetitive body movements\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"a meltdown\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"your kid\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why not say 'is there anything I can do to help?'.\\\"\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray is a patron for Autism NZ, and is passionate about raising awareness around neurodivergence.\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1842, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\", \"score\": 0.9841219471777521, \"rank\": 0.015642860837096522, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a patron\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"Autism NZ\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"awareness\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"neurodivergence\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He would love to see education around neuro differences built into the school curriculum, so that all kids learn from a young age that everyone has a unique experience of the world.\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"education\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"neuro differences\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"the school curriculum\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2030}, {\"ngram\": \"all kids\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique experience\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They'd take that knowledge with them forever\\\", he says.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that knowledge\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like so many parents of high-needs children, Murray spends a lot of time planning for his son's future.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2227, \"end\": 2233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\", \"score\": 0.9841219471777521, \"rank\": 0.015642860837096522, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many parents\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2202}, {\"ngram\": \"high-needs children\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"his son's future\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He will need a permanent carer, but I am not going to be around forever,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a permanent carer\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And that worries me, because there is no one to advocate for him on my level, it'd be terrible for the poor guy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2485, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"my level\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2448}, {\"ngram\": \"the poor guy\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The prospect of regular employment for Zac is minimal.\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2526, \"end\": 2529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"score\": 0.9997135139514457, \"rank\": 0.0002777106673353038, \"text\": \"Zac\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The prospect\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2499}, {\"ngram\": \"regular employment\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Murray has plans for a business that he can incorporate Zac into, one that plays to his son's strengths.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2546, \"end\": 2552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\", \"score\": 0.9841219471777521, \"rank\": 0.015642860837096522, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\"}, {\"begin\": 2602, \"end\": 2605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"score\": 0.9997135139514457, \"rank\": 0.0002777106673353038, \"text\": \"Zac\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zac_MacGuire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2562}, {\"ngram\": \"a business\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2577}, {\"ngram\": \"his son's strengths\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's very visual, he loves to see creation.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"creation\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's where he's the expert,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the expert\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a great outlook, but we can find some ways where it's going to actually look very, very good.\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great outlook\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2763}, {\"ngram\": \"some ways\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And at the end of the day, he's my son, and that's the only thing you can do for your kids.\\\"\", \"from\": 2842